s-liam-payne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/harry-styles-liam-payne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/harry-styles-liam-payne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/harry-styles-liam-payne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈利·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles)</a>在他的前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩 (Liam Payne)</a>英年早逝后分享了一篇悼念帖子。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：One Direction 明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>10月16日晚，据消息称利亚姆·佩恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落身亡，</a>年仅31岁。据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/oct/17/liam-payne-died-of-multiple-traumas-and-internal-and-external-bleeding" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道，阿根廷检察官办公室透露，佩恩的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>——他的头部受伤严重，足以导致死亡。</p><p>今天早些时候，One Direction 的幸存成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">扎恩·马利克 (Zayn Malik)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">尼尔·霍兰 (Niall Horan)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森 (Louis Tomlinson)</a>和哈里·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-direction-speak-out-on-the-death-of-liam-payne-were-completely-devastated-3803904">就佩恩的去世发表了一份联合声明，他们在声明中表达了他们的悲痛，并表示他们需要时间“哀悼并处理失去我们兄弟的痛苦，他是我们的兄弟”。我们深爱着。”</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3803907" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803907" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="